xercise supported JSch public APIs under Native Image and remove the remaining placeholder test.\n2. Add the missing reachability metadata for the reflectively loaded JSch implementation classes (`com.jcraft.jsch.jce.*` and related keypair/KEX classes), then rerun `./gradlew test -Pcoordinates=com.jcraft:jsch:0.1.27`.\n3. If coverage is still `0/36`, verify whether `jsch-0.1.27` lacks line-number information for these frames and decide whether this library needs manual handling because the dynamic-access reporter only sees `Unknown Source`."}}
